Text:
This movie is absolutely fantastic and the 3D Effects are used extremely well (especially when the slow-mo drugs are shown off).

@partyhardy247:
You need a 3DTV or player that supports "side-by-side" frames. I believe all standalone 3DTV's can do it and for computer solutions, there is the "Stereoscopic Player" (which also has an analgyph mode if you lack a 3DTV/Monitor).
